{"tid":1045271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將調查巴基斯坦是否使用美製F-16擊落印度戰機","createTime":"2019-03-03T13:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T14:56:22.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69dd4ff7378b6fffb25ca391ebc82eabac14e5d7","tid":1045271,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"（中央社伊斯蘭馬巴德3日綜合外電報導）美國駐伊斯蘭馬巴德大使館今天表示，美方正在尋求訊息以查證巴基斯坦是否使用美製F-16戰機擊落印度戰機，一旦屬實，可能違反巴基斯坦與美國簽定的F-16戰機銷售協議。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦表示，並未使用美製F-16戰機擊落越過克什米爾地區印巴實際控制線（Line of Control）的一架印度戰機。巴國指出，擊落印度戰機是出於自衛。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐伊斯蘭馬巴德大使館一名發言人表示：「我們知曉這些報導，正在尋求更多的訊息。我們十分嚴肅看待濫用自衛條款的所有指控。」<br />\n<br />\n美國外銷軍火時，經常添加限制條款，透過所謂的終端使用者協議，限縮軍火的使用。（譯者：嚴思祺/核稿：林治平）1080303<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201903030190.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201903030190.aspx&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=ceff6f6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201903030190.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"4dbce59a6b5108f3759ce4bbd29a2f5ef51f79f2","tid":1045271,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:15:45.000Z","msg":"人哋飛到入黎都唔打得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4385a6f0fd28489670df838cafb304dd5f04e6a0","tid":1045271,"uid":2110,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4dbce59a6b5108f3759ce4bbd29a2f5ef51f79f2","tid":1045271,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:15:45.000Z","msg":"人哋飛到入黎都唔打得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:18:31.000Z","msg":"用其他國家武器打囉，無呀？無咪唔好打囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abb7018efe5853e1d37fbc06532cb29994bcac7","tid":1045271,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"唔可以咁用F16<br />\n咁可以點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab1b2cdeb9a25dadbd308aaf5b3a76e0fc16579","tid":1045271,"uid":46245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"唔明，即係f16只能做擺設？（佢「年紀」上的確可以入博物館擺設）"},{"pid":"dd5bac637d40fe4dad15aa000ce44df284cfca56","tid":1045271,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ab1b2cdeb9a25dadbd308aaf5b3a76e0fc16579","tid":1045271,"uid":46245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"唔明，即係f16只能做擺設？（佢「年紀」上的確可以入博物館擺設）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:50:53.000Z","msg":"美國空軍啲B-52都仲飛緊"},{"pid":"6e6670b4dfebd57094c6a6dd04786aaad38b4597","tid":1045271,"uid":213597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}